                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-171-off956 t18320216-171-crimeloc958"></join>; he took a roll of flannel off the counter, and passed me with it on his shoulder; I went into the shop, and found nobody there - I called the boy up stairs, then went in pursuit, and overtook the prisoner in Rathbone-place, with the flannel on his shoulder - he made a great resistance, but I brought him back.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320216-171-person1430">
